description:
Video Tour Available
 This new construction 1 bed, 1 bath home combines modern living with one of the city's most desirable locations. This thoughtfully designed unit offers new appliances, abundant natural light, and a spacious open layout perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. The kitchen features sleek finishes and ample storage, while the bedroom provides a comfortable retreat with generous closet space.Located just 0.5 miles from South Boston's beaches, this home places you within walking distance to parks, boutique shops, and Southie's hottest restaurants and bars. Commuters will love the easy access to public transportation, major highways, the Seaport, and Downtown Boston. Don't miss the opportunity to live in a beautifully built apartment in one of Boston's most vibrant neighborhoods!
